# game/script.rpy:1040
translate malay start_a30eb804:

    # centered "Disclaimer:\n\nThis session uses some questions from the Depression Anxiety Stress Scales (DASS), specifically the stress subscale. \ These items are included for research and educational purposes only, and are not a substitute for professional diagnosis or treatment."
    centered "Penafian:\n\nSesi ini menggunakan beberapa soalan daripada Depression Anxiety Stress Scales (DASS), khususnya subskala tekanan. Item-item ini disertakan untuk tujuan penyelidikan dan pendidikan sahaja, dan bukan pengganti kepada diagnosis atau rawatan profesional."

# game/script.rpy:1085
translate malay start_8f75aff9:

    # e "Welcome back, [user_name]."
    e "Selamat datang kembali, [user_name]."

# game/script.rpy:1088
translate malay start_f19fdf45:

    # e "It's nice to see you again."
    e "Senang bertemu anda semula."

# game/script.rpy:1091
translate malay start_0ff7db9d:

    # e "Last time, it seemed like things were quite heavy for you."
    e "Sesi sebelumnya, awak nampaknya sedang mengalami masalah yang cukup berat."

# game/script.rpy:1094
translate malay start_0119b2a7:

    # e "Last time, things seemed fairly manageable."
    e "Sesi sebelumnya, masalah kamu boleh diurus."

# game/script.rpy:1098
translate malay start_0d8d085a:

    # e "Hi, I'm Hana."
    e "Hai, saya Hana."

# game/script.rpy:1102
translate malay start_b94242cf:

    # e "And you are..?"
    e "Dan siapa nama anda?"

# game/script.rpy:1110
translate malay start_5f6b6bb2:

    # e "It's nice to meet you, [user_name]."
    e "Senang bertemu dengan anda, [user_name]."

# game/script.rpy:1113
translate malay start_643fd6a3:

    # e "My name means \"flower\" in Japanese and \"happiness\" in Arabic."
    e "Hana bermaksud bunga dalam bahasa Jepun dan juga kebahagiaan dalam bahasa Arab."

# game/script.rpy:1114
translate malay start_6dd54a47:

    # e "I like to think that's a reminder to bring a little kindness into every conversation."
    e "Saya suka menganggapnya sebagai peringatan untuk membawa sedikit kebaikan dalam setiap perbualan."

# game/script.rpy:1115
translate malay start_1ad86e8c:

    # e "It's lovely to have you here."
    e "Senang bertemu di sini."

# game/script.rpy:1120
translate malay start_a0c1aa7a:

    # e "That's very kind of you to say. I'm happy to meet you too."
    e "Wah baiknya kamu. Saya juga gembira berjumpa kamu"

# game/script.rpy:1123
translate malay start_32b8e3e8:

    # e "Thank you. I've always been fond of it myself."
    e "Terima kasih."

# game/script.rpy:1126
translate malay start_3bc4dc83:

    # e "Hi. It's okay if you're not sure what to say. We can take things one step at a time."
    e "Hai. Tidak mengapa jika anda tidak pasti apa yang perlu anda katakan. Kita boleh mengambil sesuatu satu langkah pada satu masa."

# game/script.rpy:1131
translate malay start_d473672d:

    # e "So, [user_name], how have you been feeling today?"
    e "Jadi, apakah perasaan kamu hari ini?"

# game/script.rpy:1137
translate malay start_dda554b6:

    # e "That's wonderful to hear. I'm glad you're feeling good today."
    e "Itu indah untuk didengar. Saya gembira anda berasa baik hari ini."

# game/script.rpy:1142
translate malay start_ff1ff2e0:

    # e "Sometimes an ordinary day can be a good thing."
    e "Kadang-kadang hari biasa boleh menjadi perkara yang baik."

# game/script.rpy:1147
translate malay start_e410b885:

    # e "It sounds like you've had a few things weighing on your mind."
    e "Nampaknya anda mempunyai beberapa perkara yang membebankan fikiran anda."

# game/script.rpy:1152
translate malay start_0489de98:

    # e "That sounds like a lot to carry. Thank you for sharing that with me."
    e "Wah, itu kelihatan seperti banyak perkara untuk dibawa. Terima kasih kerana berkongsi itu dengan saya."

# game/script.rpy:1158
translate malay start_5d1beeff:

    # e "How has your day been so far?"
    e "Bagaimana hari anda sejauh ini?"

# game/script.rpy:1164
translate malay start_5183715f:

    # e "It sounds like you've been getting quite a lot done today. Well done."
    e "Nampaknya anda telah melaksanakan banyak perkara hari ini. Kerja yang baik."

# game/script.rpy:1169
translate malay start_39d130b3:

    # e "That sounds nice. It's good to make time for yourself now and then."
    e "Wah, itu kelihatan menyenangkan. Penting untuk meluangkan masa untuk diri sendiri dari masa ke masa."

# game/script.rpy:1174
translate malay start_c1c23b84:

    # e "I'm sorry to hear that. It sounds like today has taken a lot out of you."
    e "Saya turut sedih mendengar itu. Nampaknya hari ini telah mengambil banyak daripada anda."

# game/script.rpy:1179
translate malay start_45e61395:

    # e "That sounds difficult. Some days can feel much heavier than others."
    e "Wah, Kedengaran sukar. Beberapa hari boleh berasa jauh lebih berat daripada yang lain."

# game/script.rpy:1185
translate malay start_406e37dc:

    # e "Did anything feel stressful or frustrating for you today?"
    e "Adakah anda berasa tertekan atau mengecewakan hari ini?"

# game/script.rpy:1191
translate malay start_218b744b:

    # e "I'm glad to hear that. It sounds like today was fairly manageable."
    e "Saya gembira mendengarnya. Nampaknya hari ini agak mudah untuk anda lalui."

# game/script.rpy:1196
translate malay start_39cae270:

    # e "That's understandable. Small stresses can still add up over time."
    e "Itu boleh difahami. Tekanan kecil juga boleh terkumpul dari semasa ke semasa."

# game/script.rpy:1201
translate malay start_911eb93b:

    # e "I'm sorry to hear that. Dealing with stress throughout the day can be really tiring."
    e "Saya turut bersimpati mendengarnya. Menghadapi tekanan sepanjang hari boleh menjadi sangat memenatkan."

# game/script.rpy:1206
translate malay start_00949022:

    # e "That sounds exhausting. It must have been difficult carrying that stress for so long."
    e "Itu kedengaran sangat meletihkan. Pasti sukar untuk menanggung tekanan itu begitu lama."

# game/script.rpy:1212
translate malay start_bdaefc3e:

    # e "Before we move on, I'd like to ask about something positive."
    e "Sebelum kita teruskan, saya ingin bertanya tentang sesuatu yang positif."

# game/script.rpy:1213
translate malay start_7c34fcf2:

    # e "Even on difficult days, there can still be small moments worth holding onto."
    e "Walaupun pada hari yang sukar, masih ada saat-saat kecil yang berbaloi untuk dihargai."

# game/script.rpy:1216
translate malay start_b212719d:

    # e "What's something that has gone well for you recently?"
    e "Apakah sesuatu yang telah berjalan dengan baik untuk anda kebelakangan ini?"

# game/script.rpy:1222
translate malay start_1e54e896:

    # e "That's wonderful to hear. It's always nice to see your efforts pay off."
    e "Itu sangat menggembirakan untuk didengar. Seronok melihat usaha anda membuahkan hasil."

# game/script.rpy:1227
translate malay start_da0c51c5:

    # e "That sounds lovely. Small moments of connection can mean a great deal."
    e "Itu kedengaran sangat menyenangkan. Saat-saat kecil bersama orang lain boleh membawa makna yang besar."

# game/script.rpy:1232
translate malay start_35d0b3a5:

    # e "That's okay. When we're feeling drained, it can be difficult to notice the positive things around us."
    e "Tidak mengapa. Apabila kita berasa letih atau terbeban, kadangkala sukar untuk melihat perkara-perkara positif di sekeliling kita."

# game/script.rpy:1237
translate malay start_fd077d02:

    # e "I'm sorry to hear that. When things have been difficult for a while, it can be hard to see the brighter moments."
    e "Saya turut bersimpati mendengarnya. Apabila sesuatu telah lama menjadi sukar, kadangkala susah untuk melihat sisi yang lebih cerah."

